FEIM set to hit ~$150M in revenue by FY29, you're looking at a company growing +32% CAGR over the next 3 years. \n\nThat's just slightly less growth than a company like $RKLB that trades at 52x sales. \n\nObviously, I'm not comparing $RKLB to $FEIM. That'd be an idiotic comparison. $RKLB's TAM is infinite compared to $FEIM's niche market. \n\nBut you do have two high growth space companies trading at VERY different multiples. \n\nEven given $FEIM a 50% discount to a company like $RKLB and you're looking at a $3.75B company (vs $566M today). \n\nOr you can think of it this way. $RBC is a precision engineering component play for robotics. Yet you have $RBC trading at 10x sales with growth rates ~1/3rd of $FEIM's whilst $FEIM trades at 7x sales. \n\nI think at bare minimum $FEIM deserves ~12x multiple over time given their moat in this space and their growth. \n\n12x on $150M = $1.8B (2.5x from today). \n\nThis is a high growth component play in the space thematic. \n\nI bought before yesterday's 15% move. Admittedly lucky timing.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 2, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 35, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 4012, "createdAt": "Sat May 02 09:17:55 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 44, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050505052154966202", "displayTextRange": [0, 282], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "MMMTwealth", "url": "https://x.com/MMMTwealth", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/MMMTwealth", "id": "1630283681284669445", "name": "Oliver | MMMT Wealth (CPA)", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1726901308580364288/ZRQ_B4Mj_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1630283681284669445/1751011091", "description": "", "location": "Join 20,000+ members \ud83d\udc49", "followers": 65766, "following": 1039, "status": "", "canDm": tru